############  This is a simpleSms applicaion can be used from CLI from unix system ######
How to use thsi application
1. python sms.py 8147830733 Hi I am Dipankar
2. python sms.py -s 160by2 8147830733 Hi! Dipankar again !
3. python sms.py -s way2sms -m 8147830733 -t Yes ! Dipankar Again!!
Use: -h / --help to get help
